content: Hi Hayden, this is Emma from Cloumen. what is one task that still eats up your team is time?
Yeah, this is James and I like to automate my air cold work.
Hi James, we build tools that handle repetitive tasks automatically. what is one job you wish your team did not have to do by hand?
I would say that our receptionist agent is able to attend all our calls.
that is great your receptionist handles calls well. Would a quick follow-up chat about that make sense?
Perfect, I will send a quick email to set that up. what is the best address to reach you?
Oh, you should know my email, right?
I do not have it handy, could you share your email address with me?
